{"tid":1371210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"列車員工督察郁手打將軍澳綫車長！","createTime":"2019-07-27T08:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T18:11:22.000Z","uid":212249,"like":916,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb7f1536832b524b34d8e6a56d93242bc17bdb7","tid":1371210,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"(16:00更新 上載圖片，為保護當事人及公司設備，圖片經過模糊處理)<br />\n(有車長因聯署信被暴力對待)<br />\nAdmin收到多名消息人士確認，因為政治及聯署信問題，將軍澳綫一位車長同一位列車員工督察先口角，後來列車員工督察郁手打人，之後更揚言唔會有人做人證。<br />\n<br />\n之後據報同時幾位列車員工督察同列車員工主任追住有關車長想搶佢手機，車長逃出辦公室到隔離站長室求助，並已報警處理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67350608_476082552952708_3194582806315401216_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQl1ySTF3OZJEuXJxWux50FQ2RAVtWT6ib24-Q6OcE5XgkrH1fqoQhEW4rlDxRx_RbE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=fd895505da7385dbb349b35417c0267b&amp;oe=5DAD485B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67350608_476082552952708_3194582806315401216_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQl1ySTF3OZJEuXJxWux50FQ2RAVtWT6ib24-Q6OcE5XgkrH1fqoQhEW4rlDxRx_RbE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Dfd895505da7385dbb349b35417c0267b%26oe%3D5DAD485B&h=0bde428c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/332287080665590/photos/a.332871817273783/476082546286042/?type=3&amp;theater&amp;ifg=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F332287080665590%2Fphotos%2Fa.332871817273783%2F476082546286042%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater%26ifg%3D1&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT18WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=a439578f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/332287080665590/photos/a.332871817273783/476082546286042/?type=3&amp;theater&amp;ifg=1</a>"},{"pid":"bf78ed662ae87d658e26dd489fa3b9d362cdd4ce","tid":1371210,"uid":139704,"like":820,"dislike":4,"score":816,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 藍絲先係真暴徒<br />\n慌死佢唔係唔夠人講記出手打個咩<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"7ac27b0